2783 they had no greater favoriteson feelings last year when 
george bush beat dukakis 10026 to 9971 
joseph kennedy brought his family to hyannisport in 1926 but it 
wasnt until his son became a national figure that the sandy beaches 
and sunshine of cape cod gained national attention and later 
unrestrained development say local historians 
the beauty uniqueness and excitement of the cape portrayed by 
the press put barnstable on the map and in the world spotlight 
according to the school department narrative 
