<DOCNO> AP890109-0268 </DOCNO>
<TEXT>
for sundowners who fear the night and sleep by day families 
are often bedded down by their bedsides in inpatient hospices like 
the connecticut hospice which has its own building other hospices 
operate in a wing or ward of hospitals 
