during a hazing at alfred university in upstate new york 
their very future is in jeopardy mrs stevens says i 
think weve come to a point where the people who supervise them 
realize the problems are enormous and theyre just not sure what to 
do about it 
the problems boil down to two harddying traditions drinking 
and hazing 
critics call fraternities an anachronism 
